	<span class=\"BoldText\">Premium Presentation</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Presented by The Cultch</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Created and Performed by Ronnie Burkett (Toronto)</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Historic Theatre 1895 Venables St.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Ronnie Burkett Theatre of Marionettes is celebrating its 40th anniversary and bringing the party to The Cultch with <span class=\"ItalicText\">The Daisy Theatre: Back in Bloom!</span> Canada’s favourite puppet cabaret springs to life once again, delivering a fresh bouquet of edgy satire, unforgettable characters, and heartfelt humour. Created by Cultch favourite Ronnie Burkett, Back in Bloom features beloved Daisy Theatre stars Schnitzel, Edna Rural and Esme Massengill, alongside new characters and classic acts.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>For a night of laughter, song and surprise, come celebrate the joy of live theatre blossoming on the Historic Stage with <span class=\"ItalicText\">The Daisy Theatre: Back in Bloom!</span><span><br/></span>
""";
